name: Anthony CANN, Petitioner v. Hon. Charles J. CUNNINGHAM, III, Respondent

parties: Anthony CANN, Petitioner v. Hon. Charles J. CUNNINGHAM, III, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 7th day of May, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

91 A.3d 1233

May 7, 2014.
